    "romaji": "anata ga kono kuni o aishi, kinben ni hataraki, zeikin o osame, hou o junshu shi, soshite kono kuni no shimin ni naritai no nara, anata o hongoku e soukan shitagaru hito de wa naku, imin seido kaikaku o motomeru hito o erabu beki desu."
