    "en": "When he had rounded the curve of the dusty road that hid him from Akemi’s house, Harumi drew his horse to a stop under a clump of dogwood.",
    "romaji": "hokorippoi toori no kado o magari, akemi no ie kara sugata ga mienai tokoro made kuru to, harumi wa tazuna o hiite, hanamizuki no shigemi no shita de uma o tometa."
